ng the template available in the Submission system. Activities are expected to achieve TRL 4-5 by the end of the project. Activities may start at any TRL. Call documents Horizon Europe Work Programme 2025 Cluster 5 - Climate, Energy and MobilityHorizon Europe Work Programme 2025 Cluster 5 - Climate, Energy and Mobility(2548kB) Contact National Contact Points for Horizon Europe Website',
